# Freqtrade & FreqAI Documentation & Resources

The absolute best source for programming documentation on Freqtrade and its machine learning extension, FreqAI, is the **official documentation** hosted at [www.freqtrade.io](https://www.freqtrade.io).

Because Freqtrade is a rapidly evolving open-source project, relying on third-party blogs or older tutorials often leads to "broken code" due to breaking changes in the strategy interface (e.g., the transition from version 2 to version 3).

---

## 1. Official Freqtrade Documentation

The official site is divided into logical sections that cover everything from basic setup to advanced strategy coding.

| Section | Link | Best For |
|---------|------|----------|
| **Strategy Customization** | [freqtrade.io/strategy-customization](https://www.freqtrade.io/en/stable/strategy-customization/) | The "Bible" for programmers — IStrategy interface, candle data (OHLCV) handling via Pandas, entry/exit signals |
| **Technical Indicators** | [strategy-customization#indicators](https://www.freqtrade.io/en/stable/strategy-customization/#technical-indicators) | TA-Lib, pandas-ta, and custom technical indicators |
| **The Dataframe Ecosystem** | [strategy-customization#dataframe](https://www.freqtrade.io/en/stable/strategy-customization/#dataframe) | How Freqtrade uses Pandas dataframes to process market data without lookahead bias |

---

## 2. FreqAI Documentation

FreqAI is integrated into the main Freqtrade documentation but lives in its own high-level category.

| Section | Link | Best For |
|---------|------|----------|
| **FreqAI Introduction** | [freqtrade.io/freqai](https://www.freqtrade.io/en/stable/freqai/) | ML pipeline: Features → Labels → Training → Inference |
| **FreqAI Configuration & Models** | [freqai-configuration](https://www.freqtrade.io/en/stable/freqai-configuration/) | Class structure (IFreqaiModel), custom models with XGBoost, CatBoost, LightGBM |
| **Feature Engineering** | [freqai-feature-engineering](https://www.freqtrade.io/en/stable/freqai-feature-engineering/) | Defining parameters the AI uses to learn market patterns |

