## Pro Tip: Interface Version

Always check the `INTERFACE_VERSION` in code examples you find online. If it's **2**, you'll likely need to migrate it to version **3** using the [Strategy Interface Version](https://www.freqtrade.io/en/stable/strategy-customization/#strategy-interface-version) docs and [changelog](https://github.com/freqtrade/freqtrade/releases) to work with current versions of the bot.
